{"id":1667013,"retrievedAt":"2026-04-10T12:10:34.883Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"https://jfc.org.il/en/news_journal/62962-2/","id":1667013,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["IL"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"ארבעת הימים","overview":"An English-speaking advertisement film produced by the Information Center (Hasbara) in cooperation with the Israel Government Tourist Corporation, intended to promote international tourism to Israel’s coasts and four seas: the Mediterranean Sea, the Sea of Galilee, the Dead Sea and the Red Sea. The film presents to potential tourists the options for a beach and sea vacation in Israel, whether in the coastal cities along the Mediterranean such as Nahariya, Acre and Tel Aviv where one can fish, swim or sail, a visit to Tiberias to the shores of the Sea of Galilee where water skiing developed in recent years, and a vacation in the Dead Sea. Upon visiting the southern city of Eilat with its shores along the Red Sea, one can experience the beauty of diving, as depicted in the underwater photography of the coral reefs in Eilat.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/h8EEQuqzgDJ6CFGQXSYWmRxVHUA.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":64937,"logo_path":null,"name":"Israel Film Service","origin_country":"IL"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"IL","name":"Israel"}],"release_date":"1962-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":22,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"The Four Seas","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":8787,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Gila Almagor","original_name":"Gila Almagor","popularity":0.3854,"profile_path":"/w5X2yS6tgVVbYUwRjFenWeN25I3.jpg","cast_id":1,"character":"Self","credit_id":"69d80d5aeec40b1f865d1cf0","order":0}],"cr